337
00:30:04,470 --> 00:30:07,310
You kidnapped her.

338
00:30:08,310 --> 00:30:11,890
I didn't kidnap her; I saved her.

339
00:30:11,890 --> 00:30:14,050
That wasn't your true intention, though.

340
00:30:14,050 --> 00:30:16,600
