341
00:30:16,600 --> 00:30:18,900
What are you trying to say?

342
00:30:20,720 --> 00:30:23,600
You know that my friend and Lee Jae In broke up, right?

343
00:30:23,600 --> 00:30:26,180
Yes, I believe I heard something like that.

344
00:30:26,180 --> 00:30:30,550
The two of them... were really good together.

345
00:30:31,470 --> 00:30:33,440
And?

346
00:30:35,450 --> 00:30:38,960
Do you want to do a good deed together?

347
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:42,260
I'm not really a nice person.

348
00:30:42,260 --> 00:30:46,410
Also... I have no interest in other people's love affairs.

349
00:30:50,710 --> 00:30:53,680
That real jer—

350
00:30:53,680 --> 00:30:57,390
Fine! She can just date someone else then.

351
00:30:57,390 --> 00:31:00,630
I mean, is Lee Jae In the only man in the world?

352
00:31:03,340 --> 00:31:05,090
You look so young.

353
00:31:05,090 --> 00:31:06,530
Thank you.

354
00:31:06,530 --> 00:31:07,760
Do you like dogs?

355
00:31:07,760 --> 00:31:09,400
I like dogs very much.

356
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:12,090
I have a big dog though.

357
00:31:14,670 --> 00:31:16,260
Hobbies?

358
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:19,910
I like to read.

359
00:31:19,910 --> 00:31:21,890
What do you like?

360
00:31:21,890 --> 00:31:25,430
I like to exercise and watch movies alone.

361
00:31:38,390 --> 00:31:40,390
- Do you have a good appetite?
- Yes.

362
00:31:44,060 --> 00:31:46,990
Should we go somewhere else?

363
00:31:48,580 --> 00:31:50,680
That would be nice.

364
00:31:50,680 --> 00:31:53,350
Otherwise we'll make them uncomfortable.

365
00:32:05,770 --> 00:32:07,200
What is it?

366
00:32:07,200 --> 00:32:08,120
Cousin....

367
00:32:08,120 --> 00:32:10,150
Call me "Hyung," you punk.

368
00:32:11,330 --> 00:32:13,590
