370
00:32:20,080 --> 00:32:24,100
I owe a debt to that woman.

371
00:32:34,100 --> 00:32:37,340
I did as much as I could.

372
00:32:37,340 --> 00:32:39,400
Vicious bastard.

373
00:32:41,440 --> 00:32:44,600
Not you, your cousin.

374
00:32:46,010 --> 00:32:50,590
That's why he makes so much money. People should be vicious like him.

375
00:32:50,590 --> 00:32:53,290
My hyung endured a lot— No, no...

376
00:32:53,290 --> 00:32:56,740
My cousin.

377
00:32:56,740 --> 00:33:00,030
Then maybe he really doesn’t have feelings for her.

378
00:33:00,030 --> 00:33:02,480
Anyway, thank you for today.

379
00:33:02,480 --> 00:33:07,770
Maybe he doesn't love Da Hyeon as much as I thought.

380
00:33:07,770 --> 00:33:09,910
I was mistaken.

381
00:33:09,910 --> 00:33:13,440
But then... it would be neater in this way.

382
00:33:13,440 --> 00:33:15,420
She can meet an even better person.

383
00:33:15,420 --> 00:33:18,530
Anyway, I did everything I could.

384
00:33:18,530 --> 00:33:22,220
So if you mention the contract or the kidnapping in the media,

385
00:33:22,220 --> 00:33:24,260
