386
00:33:24,260 --> 00:33:26,700
My cousin is a really scary person.

387
00:33:26,700 --> 00:33:29,540
Yes, yes. I know that too.

388
00:33:29,540 --> 00:33:34,700
I also know that publicizing that kind of news is not good for Da Hyeon.

389
00:33:34,700 --> 00:33:39,010
So I had no plans to actually reveal any of that information on the internet from the beginning.

390
00:33:39,010 --> 00:33:42,980
Anyway, thank you. Good-bye.

391
00:33:42,980 --> 00:33:44,780
Wait a minute.

392
00:33:44,780 --> 00:33:48,130
So you were bluffing this entire time? How dare you?

393
00:33:48,130 --> 00:33:51,380
On top of threatening me?

394
00:33:51,380 --> 00:33:53,920
What do you mean threatening?

395
00:33:53,920 --> 00:33:57,330
Let's just say I was just desperate.

396
00:34:30,300 --> 00:34:33,630
[Delete this message? Cancel/Delete]

397
00:34:36,350 --> 00:34:38,140
- Do you have a good appetite?
- Yes.

398
00:34:45,110 --> 00:34:47,490
