399
00:34:50,090 --> 00:34:52,340
Managing Director, the meeting is about to start.

400
00:34:52,340 --> 00:34:54,590
Okay.

401
00:34:54,590 --> 00:34:59,320
I prepared a marketing simulation to hit the 80% target.

402
00:34:59,320 --> 00:35:00,550
First,

403
00:35:00,550 --> 00:35:04,590
we'll establish the infrastructure for the Canadian tourists.

404
00:35:04,590 --> 00:35:08,390
We'll hire a coordinator who will customize the package for Canadians.

405
00:35:11,920 --> 00:35:13,730
Managing Director?

406
00:35:15,940 --> 00:35:17,820
Managing Director?

407
00:35:20,440 --> 00:35:22,530
I'm sorry.

408
00:35:22,530 --> 00:35:26,390
