409
00:35:26,390 --> 00:35:28,560
Yes, understood.

410
00:35:45,950 --> 00:35:49,350
May I call you again?

411
00:35:53,140 --> 00:35:54,780
Yes.

412
00:36:09,480 --> 00:36:12,390
Do you like that man?

413
00:36:12,390 --> 00:36:18,530
♫ Without any words, time passed by ♫

414
00:36:21,550 --> 00:36:24,030
Why are you asking such a thing?

415
00:36:24,030 --> 00:36:26,800
