428
00:37:10,990 --> 00:37:15,370
My mother is always on my side, but she might be cold to you.

429
00:37:15,370 --> 00:37:19,180
But you can ignore everyone else.

430
00:37:19,180 --> 00:37:22,190
I may not be able to do anything for you.

431
00:37:22,190 --> 00:37:24,810
Would that be all right?

432
00:37:24,810 --> 00:37:29,250
